Subject: [PATCH 0503/1221] MLK-10818-3 ARM: dts: add audio route
 configuration for imx7d-sdb board

add audio route configuration for imx7d-sdb board.

Signed-off-by: Zidan Wang <zidan.wang@freescale.com>
[zou:Original patch taken from
git.freescale.com/imx/fsl-arm-yocto-bsp.git-b imx-3.14.52-1.1.0_ga]
Signed-off-by: zou cao <cao.zou@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d-sdb.dts |    3 +++
 1 files changed, 3 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d-sdb.dts b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d-sdb.dts
index e45f53e..c2fd1a8 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d-sdb.dts
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d-sdb.dts
@@ -97,6 +97,9 @@
 		codec-master;
 		/* JD2: hp detect high for headphone*/
 		hp-det = <2 0>;
+		audio-routing =
+			"LINPUT1", "Main MIC",
+			"Main MIC", "MICB";
 	};
 
 	sound-hdmi {
